## Validation Criteria

After implementation, the following should work:

1. Starting a match shows XI on pitch in formation layout.
1. Tapping cards toggles them between attack (gold) and defend (blue).
1. Attack/defence scores update live as cards are toggled.
1. Synergy names appear/disappear as cards move between sides.
1. Soft cap indicator shows when exceeding formation max attackers.
1. “Kick Off” resolves the increment with cascade animation.
1. Goals resolve based on attack/defence ratio vs opponent baselines.
1. 5 increments complete a match with running score.
1. Half-time allows subs, discards, and formation change.
1. Second-half between-increments allow subs and discards.
1. Injured cards cannot be committed to attack.
1. Glass/Phoenix cards that attack have fatigue risk after resolution.
1. Match result feeds back to GameShell correctly (wins/losses/shop flow).

